'''Ann Gunter''' is an art historian and Bertha and Max Dressler Professor in the [[Humanities]] at [[Northwestern University]]. Her work focuses on [[Visual culture|visual]] and [[material culture]] of the ancient [[Near East]] and neighboring parts of the eastern Mediterranean.<ref>{{cite web|title=Ann Gunter: Department of Art History - Northwestern University|url=http://www.arthistory.northwestern.edu/people/faculty/ann-gunter.html|website=www.arthistory.northwestern.edu|publisher=Northwestern University|accessdate=7 March 2017|language=en}}</ref>
